# Privacy Policy

Effective Date: 03/09/2024

## Our Commitment to Privacy

Garcia Enterprise ("we," "us," or "our") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how our mobile application, eng618 ("App"), handles your information.

## What Information Do We Collect?

We are committed to your privacy and do not collect any personal or non-personal information while you use the App. This means we do not track your usage, gather device information, or store any data related to your activity within the App.

## Security

Although we do not collect user information, we strive to maintain a secure environment for our users. [ Briefly describe any security measures you take to protect user devices and the app itself (e.g., encryption methods used to transmit data within the app, if applicable)].

## Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.

## Contact Us

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at: [support@garciaericn.com](mailto:support@garciaericn.com)
